description:
Today's episode of Human Events Daily: Fiona Hill may have committed perjury in Impeachment testimony, Rep. Adam Schiff is GRILLED on The View over #RUSSIAGATE, The White House is questioned over Jake Sullivan’s involvement in the Steele Dossier, and The media PRE-JUDGED Kyle Rittenhouse before seeing any evidence. 


Here’s your Daily dose of Human Events with @JackPosobiec
